cdata.name: Avesta
cdata.desc:
Avesta is a Proof of Work cryptocurrency using Avesta hash as itsalgorithm. Avestas blockchain is customized to work directly with Point-of-Sales and also allows public mining on any device. It is a cryptocurrency tailor-madefor Point-of-Sales and direct payments into payment processors. It also features a 2-factor mandatory security, account recovery, coin inheritance, smartcontract UI, debit card and a mobile payment platform.
